### Run Kafka + send simulated events

Prereqs: Docker, Python 3.9

```bash
# 1. Start Kafka (Docker)
docker compose up

# 2. In another terminal, create venv and install deps
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 3. Run simulator -> Kafka producer
python -m backend.kafka.kafka_producer